name: Parisienne People
description: ﻿﻿J'adore Paris! I took this picture back in July 2017 in Paris,  visiting my brother and his girlfriend who was living there at this time. It was was a nice and sunny weekend and I loved to sit in some Cafes, sippin Beers and do People-Watching. Shot on 35mm & scanned by myself (Excuse my french!) / 2032 × 2971 pixels / JPEG / 7.4 MB
